        1,
        0.0,
        0.0
      ]
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "四家丁",
        "四禁子",
        "天牢钦犯须紧守",
        "家院",
        "张夫人",
        "忠良非是知心少",
        "悲切切将儿抱",
        "李敬犹",
        "狱官",
        "禁子",
        "舍子代替天有报",
        "薛猛"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四禁子、狱官同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "狱官",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "监狱和班房，牢房有囚床。长板带夹棍，拷打犯法郎。"
        },
        {
          "character": "狱官",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无钱休告状，有钱理也长。若问阴曹府，我是活阎王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "狱官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我，天牢狱官是也。只因薛刚罪大于天，他倒不知逃往哪里去了，可怜他一门"
        },
        {
          "character": "狱官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尽在天牢。这三百八十五口，分作四监，四监又分四牢，又有许多的字号。武、"
        },
        {
          "character": "狱官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张二家，命我昼夜紧守。"
        },
        {
          "character": "狱官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，天也晚了，小心牢门吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四禁子",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四家丁抬竹笼子内藏李孝思同上，家院上，李敬犹乘马上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "静悄悄不要高声道，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恐惊奸佞查天牢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四家丁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此天牢监门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众家丁外面伺候。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四家丁带马同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家院叫开门来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（家院放抬盒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "开门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "狱官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看是何人，这时候还来叫门？问他是谁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，叫门的是谁？"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "江淮侯前来查监。"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，乃是江淮侯前来查监。"
        },
        {
          "character": "狱官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快快开门迎接。"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "侯爷请进。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李敬犹进。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "狱官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "狱官迎接侯爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有钦犯在内，速闭监门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "狱官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是、是、是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "狱官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闭门闭门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "薛猛在哪一号？"
        },
        {
          "character": "狱官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在这星字号内。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那薛猛诡计多端，本爵要亲自查点。"
        },
        {
          "character": "狱官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但凭侯爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家院将果盒留下，酒肴尽赏他们去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "狱官，侯爷赏你酒肴，抬下去饮。"
        },
        {
          "character": "狱官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，谢侯爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不用你们伺候，下去吃酒罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "狱官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，多谢侯爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "狱官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来、来、来，抬下去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四禁子",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四禁子同抬下，狱官下。李敬犹望。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快请薛家大爵主出来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大爵主，老爷有请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛猛",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛猛、张夫人同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛猛",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罪同叛逆无人保，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张夫人",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三叔惹祸惧法逃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启老爷：江淮侯在此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛猛",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，大人在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爵主出来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，爵主！夫人！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛猛、张夫人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大人吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛猛、张夫人同跪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不见你带露随朝早，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爵主！夫人吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不见你与主立功劳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "哭头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，爵主吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎奈犯罪法不饶。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忠良非是知心少"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛猛",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大人吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛猛",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忠良非是知心少"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛猛",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罪犯天条当承受，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张夫人",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可叹公婆在天牢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛猛",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "同监阻隔万山道，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛猛",
          "line_type": "哭头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，大人吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张夫人",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "父母恩高一旦抛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爵主、夫人请坐了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛猛",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大人黑夜到此，有何见教？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我等功臣俱已保奏，奈太后不准，无法可救。因此悄悄前来，救令郎出去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛猛、张夫人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大人吓，监中查得紧急，怎么救得小儿出去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "实不相瞒，我儿孝思，与令郎同年。我特来掉换。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快抱公子与我。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（家院抱出薛蛟。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛猛",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大人此言差矣。我薛氏并无恩德，如何以亲生代替小儿，舍其一死？薛家就该"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛猛",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "存后，大人就该绝了宗嗣么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "况令郎清白无罪，为何代替小儿一死？此事断断使不得吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，爵主、夫人吓！仗义替死，亦为忠义之鬼。实非虚情假意，不可迟延。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倘若被人知觉，反为有害。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛猛",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，夫人吓，大人有此天高地厚之恩，你我感恩不尽。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛猛",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大人请上，受我夫妻一拜！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，这就不敢吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛猛",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫妻九泉必相报，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大人吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张夫人",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "舍子代死恩天高。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爵主、夫人吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一朝奉君相交好，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "异姓骨肉胜同胞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "愁眉展放免悲劳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "哭头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，儿吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为父送你归阴曹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "舍子代替天有报"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "悲切切将儿抱"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "薛猛"
        },
        {
          "character": "张夫人",
          "line_type": "同唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "感大恩，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "舍亲生，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛猛、张夫人、李敬犹",
          "line_type": "同唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "神明相照，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四禁子 （内同白） 请吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛猛、张夫人、李敬犹",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（家院收薛蛟入盒内。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "狱官、禁卒喊声高。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛猛、张夫人同回头，同叹。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛猛、张夫人",
          "line_type": "同唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还念薛家汗马劳。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛猛、张夫人、李敬犹各回头，薛猛、张夫人同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "三叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，爵主！孝思！哎呀儿吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "舍子搭救薛氏后，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四禁子、狱官抬酒盘同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "狱官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢侯爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本藩一言你听着："
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "开门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天牢钦犯须紧守"
        },
        {
          "character": "四禁子",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "狱官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "送过侯爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四禁子同下，狱官下。四家丁带马同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "聊尽大义学前朝。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李敬犹回头。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李敬犹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，儿吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
